{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"37ecaa5d05","title":"在抗大纪念“七一”“七七”及突击运动总结大会上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dd263e7069","index":0,"year":1938,"month":7,"day":9,"articleId":"37ecaa5d05"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d198c8474d","type":"paragraph","text":"在抗大纪念“七一”“七七”及突击运动总结大会上的讲话！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"37ecaa5d05"},{"id":"3ff082f27a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年7月9日）突击队员是有名英雄，还有许多无名英雄，有名英雄是从无名英雄中产生的，二者不能分离。军队与人民、官长与士兵、领袖与群众的关系，也是如此[I]1938年6月，抗大学生在全校发起理接“七七”抗战一周年创造镜战突击队员的革会意赛运动，提出“向学习突击，向工作突击，向生活窦击”等口号，运动历时一个月，涌现出520名突击队员和一批模范单位。这是毛泽东在抗大纪念“七-”“七七”及突击运动总结大会上讲话的一部分。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"37ecaa5d05"}],"page":{"id":"a94eed3643","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"37ecaa5d05","start":399,"end":399}}}},"__N_SSG":true}